{"sn2.6:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 2.6 ","sn2.6:0.2":"1. Pathamavagga ","sn2.6:0.3":"Kamadasutta ","sn2.6:1.1":"Savatthinidanam. ","sn2.6:1.2":"Ekamantam thito kho kamado devaputto bhagavantam etadavoca: ","sn2.6:1.3":"“dukkaram, bhagava, sudukkaram, bhagava”ti. ","sn2.6:2.1":"“Dukkaram vapi karonti, ","sn2.6:2.2":"(kamadati bhagava) ","sn2.6:2.3":"Sekha silasamahita; ","sn2.6:2.4":"Thitatta anagariyupetassa, ","sn2.6:2.5":"Tutthi hoti sukhavaha”ti. ","sn2.6:3.1":"“Dullabha, bhagava, yadidam tutthi”ti. ","sn2.6:4.1":"“Dullabham vapi labhanti, ","sn2.6:4.2":"(kamadati bhagava) ","sn2.6:4.3":"Cittavupasame rata; ","sn2.6:4.4":"Yesam diva ca ratto ca, ","sn2.6:4.5":"Bhavanaya rato mano”ti. ","sn2.6:5.1":"“Dussamadaham, bhagava, yadidam cittan”ti. ","sn2.6:6.1":"“Dussamadaham vapi samadahanti, ","sn2.6:6.2":"(kamadati bhagava) ","sn2.6:6.3":"Indriyupasame rata; ","sn2.6:6.4":"Te chetva maccuno jalam, ","sn2.6:6.5":"Ariya gacchanti kamada”ti. ","sn2.6:7.1":"“Duggamo, bhagava, visamo maggo”ti. ","sn2.6:8.1":"“Duggame visame vapi, ","sn2.6:8.2":"Ariya gacchanti kamada; ","sn2.6:8.3":"Anariya visame magge, ","sn2.6:8.4":"Papatanti avamsira; ","sn2.6:8.5":"Ariyanam samo maggo, ","sn2.6:8.6":"Ariya hi visame sama”ti. "}